00:32:11.949 --> 00:32:13.490
If you want to go
to Mars, and that's

00:32:13.490 --> 00:32:15.430
been your dream
since you were a kid,

00:32:15.430 --> 00:32:17.700
SpaceX is the place
you go to work.

00:32:17.700 --> 00:32:21.080
If you are into electric
cars or you really

00:32:21.080 --> 00:32:25.500
care about changing the
global warming situation,

00:32:25.500 --> 00:32:26.450
you buy into that.

00:32:26.450 --> 00:32:29.120
And so there is a
sense of mission.

00:32:29.120 --> 00:32:32.390
And there's this faith in Elon.

00:32:32.390 --> 00:32:34.560
Especially now, I think.

00:32:34.560 --> 00:32:37.950
Pre-2012, he was struggling
in a lot of ways.

00:32:37.950 --> 00:32:39.910
He has hit his stride more.

00:32:39.910 --> 00:32:43.670
And so now I think there's this
real faith that if you-- you

00:32:43.670 --> 00:32:45.310
